      "rationale": "No formal quantitative equivalency analysis performed between FDA generic pump validation geometry and the target VAD device. Qualitative similarity noted in design report but no dimensional analysis or similarity parameter comparison documented. Factor not-assessed; epistemic gap at MRL 5."
    }
